        public void loadRankedStats(int season)
        Load's the player's stats involved with their rank: Abandons, Ranked Wins, Ranked Losses, Rank, Max Rank, Skill, and Skill Standard Deviation

        Use only if you wish to load a season other than the current season, overrides old ranked data

        Parameters:
        season - The season that you want the player's main.stats from, use -1 if not sure
